(4984, 181, 'rows_1_col1', 'We have a flexible approach to every client dependent on your needs. We always have honest and open talks before committing to any new business relationship, and provide an objective view on how best to support your brand.\r\n\r\nAs an independent agency we can, and do, individualise our approach to each client – it’s not a one size fits all scenario. Our focus is 100% on return on investment. We are results driven and passionate about making every penny count.\r\n<ul class=\"thumbs-list\">\r\n 	<li><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-170\" src=\"http://localhost/product-chain/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/exploratory-chat.jpg\" alt=\"exploratory-chat\" width=\"756\" height=\"457\" /><b>Exploratory Chat\r\n</b>Could be on the phone</li>\r\n 	<li><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-171 size-full\" src=\"http://localhost/product-chain/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/chemistry-meeting.jpg\" alt=\"chemistry-meeting\" width=\"756\" height=\"457\" /><b>Chemistry Meeting\r\n</b>xxx</li>\r\n 	<li><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-172 size-full\" src=\"http://localhost/product-chain/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/define-scope-of-work.jpg\" alt=\"define-scope-of-work\" width=\"756\" height=\"457\" /><strong>Define Scope of Work</strong><b>\r\n</b>Contract</li>\r\n 	<li><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-173 size-full\" src=\"http://localhost/product-chain/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/initial-strategic-planning-meeting.jpg\" alt=\"initial-strategic-planning-meeting\" width=\"756\" height=\"457\" /><strong>Initial Strategic Planning Meeting</strong><b>\r\n</b>Kickstarts the working process</li>\r\n</ul>'),
