(6566, 238, '_cs_rows', 'field_5b4f38dbdbc27'),
(6567, 238, 'extra_content', '<h2>What did Product Chain deliver?</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Advice &amp; guidance on brand positioning &amp; category management\r\nDesigned &amp; implemented the sales strategy across major multiples / wholesale\r\nSecured buyer meetings, developing trade presentations &amp; presenting pitch proposals in partnership with Cauli Rice\r\nLogistical &amp; operational support\r\nSales Forecasting &amp; Analysis\r\nPricing &amp; promotional planning\r\nManaging day-to-day communications with retail customers</li>\r\n</ul>'),
(6568, 238, '_extra_content', 'field_5b4f3ab9dbc2b'),
(6569, 238, 'cta_link', '#'),
(6570, 238, '_cta_link', 'field_5b4f3ad2dbc2c'),
(6571, 82, 'cs_rows_0_column_a', '<h2>Achieving Success</h2>\r\nWe started working with Gem Misa (co-founder of Caul Rice) in 2014 when Cauli Rice was just a concept. Within a year we had achieved listings in all five major UK multiples with over 3000 store distribution points. In fact, in 2017 Cauli rice was the fastest growing brand in the rice category rising from 48th position to 10th in the ‘largest brand rankings’ [Nielson 2017]. We continue working together to drive this outstanding growth further, launching new products and attracting more customers.'),
(6572, 82, '_cs_rows_0_column_a', 'field_5b4f391fdbc28'),
(6573, 82, 'cs_rows_0_columns_b', '<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-342 size-full\" src=\"http://localhost/product-chain/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/cauli-rice-2.jpg\" alt=\"cauli-rice\" width=\"975\" height=\"976\" />'),
(6574, 82, '_cs_rows_0_columns_b', 'field_5b4f3a4ddbc29'),
(6575, 82, 'cs_rows_0_colour', '#ffffff'),
(6576, 82, '_cs_rows_0_colour', 'field_5b4f3a7cdbc2a'),
(6577, 82, 'cs_rows_1_column_a', '<h2>Brand Positioning</h2>\r\nSo how did we achieve this success? Well it wasn’t all plain sailing…\r\n\r\nIn the beginning we worked closely with Cauli Rice to determine the best category positioning for the product and brand. Although perceived as a niche product, together we agreed to go mainstream and target the microwave ready-to-eat buyers - this bold stance paid off.'),
(6578, 82, '_cs_rows_1_column_a', 'field_5b4f391fdbc28'),
(6579, 82, 'cs_rows_1_columns_b', '<div class=\"quote quote-xl\">\r\n\r\n<span class=\"xl\">Nº1</span> Low calorie, low carb rice alternative in the UK <span class=\"name\">Kantar Worldpanel</span>\r\n\r\n</div>'),
