(6583, 82, 'cs_rows_2_column_a', '<h2>Challenging Times</h2>\r\nThere have been many challenges along the way. The production line is a world first, so not surprisingly we have faced some production and supply chain issues. Through working together closely we have overcome these hurdles and maintained a good supplier relationship with our retail customers.'),
