(7072, 252, 'rows_1_col1', '<h2 class=\"p1 fw900\"><span style=\"color: #ffffff;\">How we work</span></h2>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"color: #ffffff;\">We believe in delivering success in the right way. We pride ourselves on our strong industry reputation and want our client brands to become recognised leaders in the food &amp; drink industry too. <b>How do we do this?</b></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul class=\"icon-list\">\r\n 	<li><span style=\"color: #ffffff;\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-115\" src=\"http://localhost/product-chain/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/icon-passion.png\" alt=\"passion\" width=\"222\" height=\"194\" /></span>\r\n<span style=\"color: #ffffff;\">Passion</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"color: #ffffff;\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-113\" src=\"http://localhost/product-chain/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/icon-knowledge.png\" alt=\"knowledge\" width=\"183\" height=\"283\" /></span>\r\n<span style=\"color: #ffffff;\">Knowledge</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"color: #ffffff;\"><img class=\"wp-image-250 size-full alignnone\" src=\"http://localhost/product-chain/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/icon-collaboration-02.png\" alt=\"collaboration\" width=\"337\" height=\"219\" /></span>\r\n<span style=\"color: #ffffff;\">Collaboration</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"color: #ffffff;\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-114\" src=\"http://localhost/product-chain/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/icon-partnerships.png\" alt=\"partnerships\" width=\"281\" height=\"154\" /></span>\r\n<span style=\"color: #ffffff;\">Partnerships</span></li>\r\n 	<li><span style=\"color: #ffffff;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-251 size-full\" src=\"http://localhost/product-chain/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/icon-integrity-01.png\" alt=\"integrity\" width=\"230\" height=\"220\" /></span>\r\n<span style=\"color: #ffffff;\">Integrity</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"color: #ffffff;\">As a FMCG retail sales agency we work with you to assess the marketplace, define the <b>best positioning</b> for your products and sell your story. We also offer <b>full admin</b> and <b>operational services</b> to support your listings. Attention to detail definitely is essential in retail.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span style=\"color: #ffffff;\">We’ll support you all the way. We’ll challenge you; We’ll ask<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">  </span>questions; but we’ll always be on your side. We’ll negotiate the best deals for you and we’ll be there to help and advise. With over 25 years’ experience in the FMCG industry you can be sure you’re in safe hands.</span></p>'),
