(12906, 347, 'cs_rows_0_column_a', '<h2>Plan</h2>\r\nWell it wasn’t all plain sailing.\r\nAt the beginning we worked closely with Cauli Rice to determine the best category positioning for the product and brand. Although perceived as a niche product, together we agreed to go mainstream and target the microwave ready-to-eat buyers, and this bold stance paid off.'),
(12907, 347, '_cs_rows_0_column_a', 'field_5b4f391fdbc28'),
