(14774, 382, 'rows_3_col1', '<h2><span style=\"color: #545959;\">Company Culture</span></h2>\r\nThe team at Product Chain are truly dedicated to their roles and work smart to deliver the very best results for our clients.\r\n\r\nWe’re a friendly bunch and are open and collaborative in our approach. You’ll always be able to get hold of someone at Product Chain and if we say we’ll call or email we will.\r\n\r\nWe believe in working in partnership with our clients and will always support and empower you to move forward. You will stay 100% in control of your brand with the addition of an experienced sales force and trusted adviser by your side.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-176\" style=\"position: relative; z-index: 10;\" src=\"http://localhost/product-chain/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/company-culture.jpg\" alt=\"company-culture\" width=\"1546\" height=\"1037\" />'),
