(15915, 390, 'rows_1_col1', '<h2><span style=\"color: #545959;\">Accelerate Your Brand Ambitions</span></h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nAs an FMCG sales agency, we have a proven track record launching new brands into the UK. We cover grocery and pharmacy multiples, independents, forecourts, wholesalers, cash &amp; carry and food service channels. We have specialists in each of these areas.\r\n\r\nAt Product Chain we offer a tailor-made service to each of our clients allowing you to select a full service contract or pick the areas that are of most worth to you. Throughout, we retain our focus and fervour, reaching all major retailers through our expertise and extensive network of industry contacts.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"animate-element alignnone wp-image-389 size-full\" src=\"http://localhost/product-chain/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/business-channel-development.png\" alt=\"Business Channel Development: New Product Launch | Channel Admin &amp; Support | Consultancy Services\" width=\"1851\" height=\"1169\" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Designed to offer the appropriate platform to provide total support to your business, at whatever stage you are. </strong>'),
