(21444, 485, 'extra_content_2_content', '<h2>What did Product Chain deliver?</h2>\r\n<ul class=\"arrows\">\r\n 	<li>Advice &amp; guidance on brand positioning &amp; category management</li>\r\n 	<li>Planning &amp; implementation of the sales strategy across major multiples &amp; wholesale</li>\r\n 	<li>Buyer meetings, trade presentations &amp; pitch proposals in partnership with Cauli Rice</li>\r\n 	<li>Logistic &amp; operational support</li>\r\n 	<li>Sales forecasting &amp; analysis</li>\r\n 	<li>Pricing &amp; promotional planning</li>\r\n 	<li>Management of day-to-day communications with retail customers</li>\r\n 	<li>Data analysis to support bids for store extensions &amp; NPD listings</li>\r\n</ul>'),
