(21484, 486, 'extra_content_0_content', '<blockquote><strong>‘Product Chain’s dedicated sales team have invaluable experience dealing with UK Grocery multiples which has saved us time and anguish along the way. Their intelligent analysis and use of the data has enabled us to work together to formulate the overall strategy for our brand. In addition, the Product Chain Client Service team have been a huge help – I did not realise how much heavy administration is required for dealing with supermarkets! They have freed up my time to concentrate on other essential areas of the business’</strong>\r\n\r\nGem Misa, Co-founder</blockquote>'),
