(21945, 501, 'cs_rows_1_column_a', '<h2>Launch</h2>\r\nPrice positioning within Food Service can often be challenging due to the multiple tiers to get to shelf. Accordingly, we advised some practical packaging changes to achieve a more appealing price point. Working together we achieved this and subsequently landed deals with Bidfood, Brakes and Compass, opening the door to thousands of food service sites nationwide.'),
(21946, 501, '_cs_rows_1_column_a', 'field_5b4f391fdbc28'),
