(21948, 501, '_cs_rows_1_columns_b', 'field_5b4f3a4ddbc29'),
(21949, 501, 'cs_rows_2_column_a', '<h2>Growing Distribution</h2>\r\nOn the supermarket front we debated whether the same strategy would work. Following a meeting with Tesco we discussed a slightly different format to offer the greatest consumer appeal. Together, with a well-thought out proposition, supported by market data we achieved a listing in almost 700 Tesco stores (Summer 2018).'),
(21950, 501, '_cs_rows_2_column_a', 'field_5b4f391fdbc28'),
