(22332, 524, 'cs_rows_0_column_a', '<h2>A Brief History</h2>\r\nOur paths crossed in 2010 when Henry and Glyn (co-founders) had their GOOD Oil listed in Waitrose and were looking to launch a brand new hemp milk alternative onto the market. Not an easy task when the milk alternative category was barely born and hemp was associated in most consumer minds with marijuana. Product Chain were brought on board to manage the sales function and make the plan a reality.'),
