(22535, 532, 'cs_rows_0_column_a', '<h2>The Plan</h2>\r\nThe challenge to Product Chain was to maintain the core health food market whilst launching 9 bar into the major multiples. At the time the cereal bar market was in decline so we worked with Wholebake to differentiate the 9 Bar range with a unique proposition and visual identity. The 9 bar team did a great job. The new packaging was modern, eye-catching and had mass appeal. This enabled our sales experts to create a strong and persuasive product pitch to sell into key buyers.'),
(22536, 532, '_cs_rows_0_column_a', 'field_5b4f391fdbc28'),
(22537, 532, 'cs_rows_0_columns_b', '<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-528 size-full\" src=\"http://localhost/product-chain/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/40g_original_multipack_plus4-copy.jpg\" alt=\"40g_original_multipack\" width=\"900\" height=\"900\" />'),
(22538, 532, '_cs_rows_0_columns_b', 'field_5b4f3a4ddbc29'),
(22539, 532, 'cs_rows_1_column_a', '<h2>Channel Strategy</h2>\r\nWe developed a bespoke channel strategy for mainstream grocery, confident that this channel required a different approach to the health food trade. Our strategy paid off and we gained listings across all the major multiples.'),
(22540, 532, '_cs_rows_1_column_a', 'field_5b4f391fdbc28'),
(22541, 532, 'cs_rows_1_columns_b', '<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-529 size-full\" src=\"http://localhost/product-chain/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/50g_flax_display_case-copy.jpg\" alt=\"50g_flax_display_case\" width=\"900\" height=\"900\" />'),
(22542, 532, '_cs_rows_1_columns_b', 'field_5b4f3a4ddbc29'),
(22543, 532, 'cs_rows_2_column_a', '<h2>Growing Sales</h2>\r\nFollowing the initial success of our sales plan we worked as a united team to develop compelling NPD including new pack formats as well as recipe variants. We analysed market data along the way to produce compelling evidence, persuading buyers to increase store listings and distribution.'),
(22544, 532, '_cs_rows_2_column_a', 'field_5b4f391fdbc28'),
(22545, 532, 'cs_rows_2_columns_b', '<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-530 size-full\" src=\"http://localhost/product-chain/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/50g_organic_display_case-copy.jpg\" alt=\"50g_flax_display_case\" width=\"900\" height=\"900\" />'),
(22546, 532, '_cs_rows_2_columns_b', 'field_5b4f3a4ddbc29'),
(22547, 532, 'cs_rows_3_column_a', '<h2>Results</h2>\r\nBy 2014 we had achieved 10,000 fixture facings in major multiples and sales continued to grow by as much as +65% yoy. By 2014, 9 Bar sales revenue had grown to over £4m from a base of £200k.'),
(22548, 532, '_cs_rows_3_column_a', 'field_5b4f391fdbc28'),
(22549, 532, 'cs_rows_3_columns_b', '<div class=\"quote quote-xl\">\r\n\r\n<span class=\"xl\">10,000</span> fixture facings in major multiples\r\n\r\n</div>'),
(22550, 532, '_cs_rows_3_columns_b', 'field_5b4f3a4ddbc29'),
(22551, 532, 'cs_rows_4_column_a', '<h2>Moving On</h2>\r\nOur partnership with Wholebake came to an end when the company was sold to enable implementation of the next phase in their ambitious growth plan. We’re glad to say, however, that we still have a good relationship with the team at Wholebake and keep in touch regularly.'),
