(22828, 547, 'cs_rows_1_column_a', '<h2>The Plan</h2>\r\nOur first step was to conduct a full review of the Chewy Vites range. We subsequently recommended some changes to increase appeal to the UK consumer. This included adapting pack size and format and removing sugar coatings from the product itself.'),
