(13, 1, '2018-06-28 11:44:08', '2018-06-28 10:44:08', '<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">About Us</h1>\r\n<h4><span style=\"color: #ff6900;\">Whether you’re a start up with a great product, or an international business looking to launch your range in the UK, we’re here to guide and support. </span></h4>\r\nProduct Chain is not just a sales agency. We’re a team of extremely experienced and passionate foodies who excel in gaining traction for challenger food and drink brands within the UK. With over twenty-five years FMCG experience we have a wide network of influential contacts and access to extensive resources and specialist knowledge, which all combine to help you achieve and grow retailer listings.', 'About Us', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'about-us', '', '', '2018-08-09 13:14:21', '2018-08-09 12:14:21', '', 0, 'http://localhost/product-chain/?page_id=13', 0, 'page', '', 0),
