(314, 1, '2018-07-24 17:06:56', '2018-07-24 16:06:56', '<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">Account Management</h1>\n<h4><span style=\"color: #ff6900;\">Retail is detail.</span></h4>\nPersuading a buyer to list your product is a huge achievement, but to ensure your product actually ends up on shelf involves a great deal of admin, process and attention to detail. If you are not set up to manage all these elements yourself our Admin &amp; Support team are available to manage these day-to-day essentials for you. We have established processes in place to streamline your order processing and issue invoices to enable smooth trading with your customers and safeguard your cash flow.', 'Account Management', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '23-autosave-v1', '', '', '2018-07-24 17:06:56', '2018-07-24 16:06:56', '', 23, 'http://localhost/product-chain/23-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
