(461, 1, '2018-08-13 16:12:50', '2018-08-13 15:12:50', '<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">New Product Launches</h1>\r\n<h4><span style=\"color: #ff6900;\">We’re passionate about delivering new food and drink innovation.</span></h4>\r\n<h4><span style=\"color: #ff6900;\">You’ve developed a fantastic product that looks and tastes great, but how do you get it on retailer shelves?</span></h4>\r\nThere are many hurdles to overcome in the process. A well thought out strategy from the start will help you clear those hurdles as painlessly as possible. This is a process we are very familiar with. We’ve learnt many lessons along the way and apply our learnings to ensure your journey will be as smooth as possible. We’ll help guide you every step of the way and offer practical advice.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class=\"curve__bottom-right alignnone wp-image-392 size-full\" src=\"http://localhost/product-chain/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/new-products.jpg\" alt=\"new-products\" width=\"1280\" height=\"574\" />', 'New Product Launches', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '21-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-08-13 16:12:50', '2018-08-13 15:12:50', '', 21, 'http://localhost/product-chain/21-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(462, 1, '2018-08-13 16:16:11', '2018-08-13 15:16:11', '<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">Business Channel Development</h1>\r\n<h4 class=\"p1\"><span style=\"color: #ff6900;\">Accelerate Your Business Plan Today<span class=\"s1\">. </span></span></h4>\r\n<p class=\"p3\">Sales is at the core of our business and we are very good at it. Our <strong>Sales Team</strong> have many years of experience drawn from Blue Chip FMCG companies and entrepreneurial backgrounds. They are dedicated to your success and will use their wide network of connections to deliver your brand goals.</p>\r\n<p class=\"p3\">Our reputation for presenting well thought out, quality product propositions means doors are open to us that may be closed to unknown brands.</p>\r\n<p class=\"p3\">We work across many brands and categories which works to your benefit. It allows us to take advantage of ad hoc opportunities as they arise and achieve more face-time with buyers. We can also draw on experiences cross-category to maximise all avenues available.</p>\r\n<p class=\"p3\">Each of our clients has a dedicated <strong>Account Lead</strong> and a dedicated <strong>Customer Service Liaison Manager</strong>. We take pride in our high levels of customer service and would be happy to supply references to support this.</p>', 'Business Channel Development', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '295-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-08-13 16:16:11', '2018-08-13 15:16:11', '', 295, 'http://localhost/product-chain/295-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(463, 1, '2018-08-13 16:18:17', '2018-08-13 15:18:17', '<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">Account Management</h1>\r\n<h4><span style=\"color: #ff6900;\">Retail is Detail.</span></h4>\r\nPersuading a buyer to list your product is a huge achievement, but to ensure your product actually ends up on shelf involves a great deal of admin, process and attention to detail. If you are not set up to manage all these elements yourself our <strong>Admin &amp; Support</strong> team are available to manage these day-to-day essentials for you. We have established processes in place to streamline your order processing and issue invoices to enable smooth trading with your customers and safeguard your cash flow.', 'Account Management', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '23-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-08-13 16:18:17', '2018-08-13 15:18:17', '', 23, 'http://localhost/product-chain/23-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
