(465, 1, '2018-08-13 16:24:12', '2018-08-13 15:24:12', '<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">The Product Chain Process</h1>\r\n<h4><span style=\"color: #ff6900;\">Loreperf ereprerum quos endae volupienda conse sectus, neseque num ipis as reproribus dollam eum re sum.</span></h4>\r\nWe met the CanO Water team in the summer of 2017 and instantly felt that we could offer a great deal to such a well timed and beautifully designed product. In a climate where we are all concerned about the negative impact of plastic on the environment, the idea of water in a can clearly offered huge potential if positioned correctly.', 'The Product Chain Process', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '324-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-08-13 16:24:12', '2018-08-13 15:24:12', '', 324, 'http://localhost/product-chain/324-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(466, 1, '2018-08-13 16:33:21', '2018-08-13 15:33:21', '<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">The Product Chain Process</h1>\n<h4><span style=\"color: #ff6900;\">Loreperf ereprerum quos endae volupienda conse sectus, neseque num ipis as reproribus dollam eum re sum.</span></h4>\nWe met the CanO Water team in the summer of 2017 and instantly felt that we could offer a great deal to such a well timed and beautifully designed product. In a climate where we are all concerned about the negative impact of plastic on the environment, the idea of water in a can clearly offered huge potential if positioned correctly.', 'The Product Chain Process', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '324-autosave-v1', '', '', '2018-08-13 16:33:21', '2018-08-13 15:33:21', '', 324, 'http://localhost/product-chain/324-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(467, 1, '2018-08-13 16:33:44', '2018-08-13 15:33:44', '<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">The Product Chain Process</h1>\r\n<h4><span style=\"color: #ff6900;\">Developing a new product is just the first step. There are many more hurdles to overcome if you want to see that product on the shelves of big national retailers.</span></h4>\r\nPassionate entrepreneurs drive exciting food and drink innovation. However, many of these entrepreneurs do not come from an FMCG or retail background. So how do you know the process to get a product onto supermarket shelves? As the saying goes ‘<strong>you don’t know what you don’t know’</strong>.\r\n\r\nWell that’s where we come in. At Product Chain food and drink retail is our lifeblood. We can help guide you through the process, and believe us, there is a process. Big companies like Tesco, Sainsbury’s and Boots have many procedures and time-plans that must be followed to maximise the chance of a successful listing.\r\n\r\nWe’ve pulled together a topline process guide below to show the different stages we walk all our clients through to help achieve sales success.', 'The Product Chain Process', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '324-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-08-13 16:33:44', '2018-08-13 15:33:44', '', 324, 'http://localhost/product-chain/324-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
